%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESununu%20said%20Trump's%20frontrunner%20status%20won't%20shift%20if%20GOP%20candidates%20aren't%20willing%20to%20go%20after%20him.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20NH%20GOP%20governor%20pointed%20to%20a%20poll%20that%20showed%20Trump%20with%2037%25%20of%20the%20primary%20vote%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThat's%2060%25%20of%20the%20voters%20right%20now%20that%20are%20not%20with%20Trump%20in%20New%20Hampshire%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20Fox%20News.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGov.%20Chris%20Sununu%20on%20Saturday%20said%20that%20the%20crop%20of%20GOP%20presidential%20candidates%20going%20up%20against%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20can%20defeat%20the%20ex-commander-in-chief%20if%20they're%20willing%20to%20go%20after%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20Hampshire%20Republican%20%E2%80%94%20who%20flirted%20with%20a%202024%20presidential%20bid%20before%20opting%20out%20and%20who%20last%20week%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.concordmonitor.com%2FSununu-not-running-for-fifth-term-as-governor-51689481%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20would%20not%20seek%20reelection%20to%20a%20fifth%20term%20in%20office%20%E2%80%94%20said%20on%20Fox%20News%20that%20the%20presidential%20candidates%20had%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20%26quot%3Bswing%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Btake%20the%20punch%26quot%3B%20if%20they%20actually%20want%20to%20dethrone%20Trump%20from%20his%20national%20frontrunner%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20conversation%2C%20Sununu%20brought%20up%20a%20recent%20University%20of%20New%20Hampshire%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscholars.unh.edu%2Fsurvey_center_polls%2F749%2F%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20showed%20Trump%20in%20the%20lead%20at%2037%25%2C%20which%20is%20well%20below%20a%20majority.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20GOP%20primary%20voters%20were%20split%20among%20the%20other%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%20of%20Florida%20was%20in%20second%20plac