Force.%20That'll%20be%20great%20for%20future%20marketing%20of%20your%20aircraft%2C'%26quot%3B%20Alperovitch%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20even%20if%20Stockholm%20approves%20the%20delivery%20of%20Gripens%20to%20Kyiv%2C%20finding%20aircraft%20to%20send%20may%20not%20be%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20six%20countries%20that%20fly%20the%20jet%2C%20only%20Sweden%20and%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20have%20backed%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20war.%20Brazil%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20Thailand%20are%20neutral%2C%20while%20Hungary%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Faustria-hungary-weapons-military-aid-ukraine-1778151%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunwilling%20to%20give%20weapons%20to%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Fhungary-doesnt-want-20-billion-euro-fund-ukraine-military%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethreatened%20to%20block%20EU%20military%20aid%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Kyiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Czech%20JAS-39%20Gripen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F633c4a766427060019ef3697%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221328%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Czech%20JAS-39%20Gripen%20during%20an%20exercise%20in%20June%202018.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20National%20Guard%2FTech.%20Sgt.%20Mindy%20Bloem%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Czech%20Republic%20has%2014%20Gripen%20Cs%20and%202%20Gripen%20Ds%20under%20lease%20until%202027%2C%20when%20they%20will%20be%20replaced%20by%20F-35s.%20Its%20only%20other%20combat%20aircraft%20are%2016%20Aero%20L-159%20subsonic%20light%20aircraft%2C%20but%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20is%20also%20surrounded%20by%20allies%2C%20which%20could%20make%20it%20more%20willing%20to%20part%20with%20some%20of%20its%20jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESweden%20operates%20about%2080%20Gripen%20Cs%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3