ion%20concept%20shows%20the%20golden%20color%20cryptocurrency%20coins%20put%20on%20the%20blue%20color%20background%20with%20the%20shade%20of%20shadow%20for%20creating%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20digital%20currency%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64bacc9903c40c001a983142%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENamthip%20Muanthongthae%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBitcoin%20could%20soar%20above%20%24120%2C000%20if%20miners%20keep%20holding%20onto%20tokens%2C%20Standard%20Chartered%20analyst%20Geoff%20Kendrick%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Insider%2C%20he%20acknowledged%20bitcoin's%20price%20gains%20help%20fuel%20a%20positive-feedback%20loop.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20your%20point%20about%20this%20becoming%20self-fulfilling%2C%20I%20suspect%20is%20actually%20a%20very%20important%20driver.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcurrencies%2Fbcc-usd%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%3EBitcoin%3C%2Fa%3E%20miners%20are%20creating%20a%20virtuous%20circle%20that%20could%20propel%20the%20token's%20price%20beyond%20already-bullish%20forecasts%2C%20Standard%20Chartered%20analyst%20Geoff%20Kendrick%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20as%20miners%20often%20sell%20fewer%20tokens%20when%20the%20price%20climbs%2C%20a%20bullish%20tendency%20that%20led%20him%20say%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-outlook-120000-crypto-mining-profit-btc-sales-2023-7%5C%22%3E%24120%2C000%20is%20possible%20next%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20representing%20300%25%20upside%20from%20current%20levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20follow-up%20interview%2C%20Insider%20asked%20Kendrick%3A%20if%20higher%20prices%20cause%20miners%20to%20sell%20fewer%20tokens%2C%20further%20boosting%20prices%2C%20then%20would%20even%20higher%20prices%20fuel%20a%20positive-feedback%20loop%20that%20takes%20bitcoin%20past%20%24120%2C000%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20your%20point%20about%20this%20becoming%20self-fulfilling%2C%20I%20suspect%20is%20actually%20a%20very%20important%20driver%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiners%20predominantly%20sell%20bitcoin%20to%20cover%20costs.%20But%20as%20the%20price%20rises%20and%20previous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fcore-scientific-shut-down-thousands-bankrupt-celsius-bitcoin-mining-rigs-2023-1%5C%22%3Edebt%20struggles%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20industry%20ebb%20away%2C%20miners%20are%20letting%20go%20of%20less%20bitcoin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20tailwind%20is%20the%20coin's%20upcoming%20halving%20in%202024%2C%20which%20is%20when%20the%20reward%20given%20to%20miners%20is%20cut%20in%20half.%20This%20is%20to%20cap%20the%20supply%20of%20bitcoins%2C%20and%20has%20historically%20led%20to%20price%20increases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20if%20you%20add%20in%20some%20of%20the%20other%20things%2C%20like%20getting%20close%20to%20the%20halving%20cycle%2C%20et%20cetera%2C%20then%20that%20sort%20of%20adds%2C%26quot%3B%20Kendrick%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20yeah%2C%20the%20cycle%20in%20theory%20just%20keeps%20going.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiners%20also%20have%20little%20reason%20outside%20of%20bitcoin's%20price%20moves%20to%20sell%20the%20token%2C%20he%20said.%20Some%20of%20this%20is%20on%20account%20of%20the%20culture%20surrounding%20the%20industry%2C%20with%20many%20miners%20holding%20on%20in%20the%20anticipation%20that%20bitcoin%20eventually%20reaches%20stellar%20highs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20they%20basically%20want%20to%20have%20a%20company%20that%20starts%20out%20when%20prices%20are%20cheap%2C%20get%20cheaper%20electricity%20and%20stuff%2C%20and%20then%20hold%20on.%20It's%20like%20a%20super-leveraged%20play%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKendrick%20has%20been%20bullish%20on%20bitcoin%20this%20year%2C%20and%20in%20April%20he%20said%20it%20would%20hit%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Fbitcoin-could-soar-268-100-174339674.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24100%2C000%20in%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20a%20number%20of%20other%20factors%20beyond%20miner%20profitability.%20Examples%20included%20bitcoin's%20safe-haven%20reputation%2C%20regulatory%20adaptations%2C%20institutional%20interest%2C%20alternative%20currency%20fall-off%2C%20and%20less%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%20told%20Insider%20that%20a%20few%20of%20these%20factors%20also%20suggest%20more%20upside.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20BlackRock's%20interest%20in%20creating%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-crypto-blackrock-larry-fink-wall-street-love-hate-relationship-2023-7%5C%22%3Ebitcoin%20spot%20ETF%3C%2Fa%3E%20signals%20growing%20demand%20from%20the%20investment%20firm's%20clients%2C%20while%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20expected%20end%20on%20its%20rate-hiking%20cycle%20would%20marginally%20help%20bitcoin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20factor%20that%20Kendrick%20would%20reassess%20was%20his%20idea%20that%20bitcoin%20would%20gain%20from%20disinvestment%20in%20other%20crypto%2C%20or%20so-called%20altcoins.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20he%20noted%20the%20recent%20courtroom%20victory%20of%20Ripple%20over%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%2C%20which%20sued%20the%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fripple-seeks-internal-sec-records-xrp-legality-securities-bitcoin-ether-2021-3%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3Ein%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20its%20cryptocurrency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcurrencies%2Fxrp-usd%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3EXRP%