stry%20for%20a%20few%20years%2C%20I%20decided%20in%20my%2030s%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20my%20own%20company.%20I%20was%20fed%20up%20working%20so%20hard%20for%20others%20and%20not%20reaping%20the%20full%20benefits%20of%20what%20I%20was%20putting%20into%20someone%20else's%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20a%20long%20time%20to%20think%20of%20an%20idea.%20I'm%20not%20religious%2C%20but%20I%20prayed%20for%20a%20sign%20that%20would%20point%20me%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20a%20moneymaking%20idea.%20In%202021%2C%20I%20had%20a%20dream%20that%20I%20helped%20my%20friend%2C%20an%20ex-porn%20star%2C%20sell%20her%20breast%20implants.%20When%20I%20told%20her%20about%20the%20dream%2C%20she%20thought%20it%20could%20be%20a%20brilliant%20business%20idea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20started%20researching%20platforms%20that%20sold%20used%20items%20from%20people%20in%20the%20adult%20industry.%20Each%20website%20I%20found%20seemed%20outdated%20or%20didn't%20provide%20a%20good%20user%20experience%20for%20buyers%20or%20sellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20adult%20stars%20can%20sell%20their%20items%20themselves%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20challenges.%20They%20have%20to%20handle%20all%20the%20logistics%2C%20including%20shipping%20and%20customer%20service%2C%20and%20they%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20much%20to%20price%20each%20item.%20Most%20of%20these%20stars%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20do%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20launch%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffansutopia.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFans%20Utopia%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20that%20people%20could%20buy%20their%20favorite%20adult%20or%20porn%20star's%20used%20panties%2C%20socks%2C%20lingerie%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20the%20business%20by%20cold-calling%20adult-industry%20stars%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20no%20experience%20in%20the%20adult%20industry%2C%20so%20when%20I%20launched%20the%20business%2C%20I%20first%20turned%20to%20my%20ex-porn-star%20friend%20for%20help.%20I%20asked%20her%20for%20a%20list%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20porn%20stars'%20names.%20Then%20I%20sent%20them%20messages%20on%20social%20media%20explaining%20more%20about%20the%20company%20and%20how%20they%20could%20make%20money%20from%20the%20used%20items%20they%20had%20lying%20around%20after%20video%20or%20photo%20shoots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20reason%20these%20stars%20decided%20to%20work%20with%20me%20was%20that%20they%20spent%20so%20much%20money%20on%20lingerie%20that%20they%20wore%20only%20a%20few%20times.%20I%20facilitated%20a%20way%20for%20them%20to%20sell%20these%20items%20for%20cash%20so%20that%20they%20didn't%20have%20to%20throw%20them%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Natasha%20Root%2C%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64baf9555adc5f001951d6e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221137%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENatasha%20Root%20never%20shames%20her%20customers%20for%20their%20fetish%20or%20requests%2C%20and%20says%20her%20business%20is%20a%20safe%20space.%3Cp%3ENatasha%20Root%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%C2%A0%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20take%20care%20of%20all%20the%20dirty%20work%20to%20sell%20these%20used%20items%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20this%20business%20to%20be%20a%20full-service%20company.%20We%20do%20everything%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20adult%20stars%20since%20they%20are%20often%20so%20busy%20traveling%20and%20shooting%20content%20for%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20we%20build%20a%20landing%20page%20for%20that%20person%20so%20that%20all%20their%20items%20can%20be%20found%20in%20one%20place%20if%20a%20customer%20comes%20on%20our%20website%20and%20searches%20their%20name.%20My%20team%20often%20meets%20the%20star%2C%20or%20they%20come%20to%20our%20offices%20to%20drop%20off%20the%20items%20that%20they%20want%20to%20sell.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ask%20them%20to%20share%20information%20about%20each%20item%2C%20including%20when%20the%20item%20was%20used%20(whether%20for%20a%20specific%20scene%20or%20personal%20use)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20any%20photos%20they%20have%20of%20themselves%20using%20or%20wearing%20the%20items.%20We%20then%20take%20photos%20of%20the%20items%20and%20store%20them%20in%20our%20warehouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20price%20the%20items%20based%20on%20a%20gut%20feeling%20and%20how%20interesting%20they%20are%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20list%20a%20few%20items%20(and%20up%20to%2025)%20at%20a%20time%20for%20a%20person%20on%20their%20page%2C%20and%20once%20the%20items%20are%20live%2C%20we%20share%20the%20page%20link%20with%20the%20adult%20star.%20The%20best%20marketing%20is%20often%20when%20they%20share%20the%20link%20on%20social%20media%20%E2%80%94%20most%20buyers%20find%20us%20from%20Reddit%20and%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20buyers%20have%20special%20requests%20or%20want%20to%20purchase%20a%20specific%20item%20from%20a%20star.%20For%20example%2C%20one%20buyer%20wanted%20used%20breast%20implants%20from%20Mia%20Malkova%2C%20so%20we%20completed%20the%20request%20and%20sold%20them%20for%20%242%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20payment%20goes%2C%20each%20star%20has%20a%20negotiated%20rate%20that%20they%20get%20when%20their%20items%20sell.%20Since%20there's%20no%20industry%20standard%20for%20how%20much%20to%20price%20different%20items%2C%20I%20usually%20list%20them%20based%20on%20what%20I%20think%20they%20should%20cost%20or%20compare%20the%20item%20with%20another%20one%20that%20sold%20for%20a%20certain%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20think%20about%20doing%20this%20auction-style%2C%20but%20it%20wouldn't%20work.%20Most%20buyers%20want%20to%20buy%20one%20item%20and%20not%20have%20to%20play%20a%20bidding%20game%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertain%20items%20sell%20for%20more%3A%20Panties%20that%20have%20been%20soiled%20with%20period%20blood%2C%20sweat%2C%20or%20urine%2C