0on%20their%20lingerie%20and%20panties%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20get%20them%20a%20price%20that%20they%20deserve.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20payment%20split%20depends%20on%20the%20adult%20star's%20agreement%20with%20us%2C%20but%20they%20take%20between%2040%25%20and%2060%25%20of%20the%20sale.%20We%20feel%20that's%20fair%20since%20we%20do%20all%20the%20marketing%2C%20shipping%2C%20selling%2C%20and%20customer%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20adult%20stars%20are%20happy%20to%20sell%20these%20items%20because%20they%20would%20normally%20just%20throw%20them%20away%20or%20store%20them%20in%20a%20closet.%20Every%20star%20is%20different%2C%20and%20what%20sells%20for%20them%20depends%20on%20what%20they're%20known%20for%20in%20the%20porn%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20business%20has%20made%20me%20a%20successful%20entrepreneur%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20misunderstood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20I've%20sold%20thousands%20of%20items%20worldwide%20and%20been%20able%20to%20grow%20this%20into%20a%20legitimate%20six-figure%20business.%20In%20addition%2C%20we%20grew%20out%20of%20our%20old%20space%20and%20moved%20into%20a%20warehouse%20space%20in%20Westlake%20Village%2C%20California%2C%20that's%20over%202%2C000%20square%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20fetish%20and%20adult%20industry%20is%20misunderstood.%20Of%20course%2C%20some%20people%20think%20what%20I%20do%20is%20disturbing%2C%20but%20everyone%20has%20sex%2C%20and%20everyone%20has%20their%20own%20little%20quirks.%20You%20shouldn't%20shame%20people%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hope%20one%20day%20it's%20not%20so%20looked%20down%20upon%20and%20that%20this%20business%20is%20recognized%20for%20what%20it%20is%3A%20a%20way%20for%20adult%20stars%20to%20connect%20with%20their%20fans%20and%20make%20some%20extra%20money%20that%20they%20deserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you've%20made%20money%20working%20an%20unusual%20job%2C%20email%20Jenna%20Gyimesi%20at%20%3Ca%20re