the%20sale%20price%2C%20and%20any%20promotions%20in%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEagle-eyed%20shoppers%20also%20notice%20the%20cents%20section%20of%20the%20price%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-prices-tags-explained-2018-4%5C%22%3Eused%20to%20indicate%20certain%20markdowns%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Prices%20ending%20in%20.99%20are%20full-price%2C%20while%2097s%20indicate%20clearance%20deals.%20Double%20eights%20or%20zeroes%20indicate%20manager%20markdowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20cards%20will%20also%20show%20a%20small%20asterisk%20in%20the%20upper%20right-hand%20corner%2C%20which%20fans%20of%20the%20brand%20have%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3Bstar%20of%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222351%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Costco%20price%20tags%20showing%20an%20asterisk%20fans%20call%20the%20%26quot%3Bstar%20of%20death%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b96e31245f83001904e2dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221763%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECustomers%20shop%20for%20clothing%20at%20a%20Costco%20store%20in%20Novato%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20understand%20the%20cryptic%20symbol's%20significance%2C%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20a%20manager%20in%20Texas%20who%20has%20been%20with%20the%20company%20for%20over%2020%20years.%20Insider%20has%20verified%20his%20identity%20but%20is%20keeping%20it%20anonymous%20as%20he%20is%20not%20authorized%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20starters%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI've%20literally%20never%20ever%20in%20my%20life%20referred%20to%20it%20as%20the%20'star%20of%20death.'%20If%20you%20work%20at%20Costco%20and%20you%20see%20the%20if%20you%20see%20the%20asterisk%2C%20you%20just%20say%20it's%20'pending%20delete.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPending%20delete%26quot%3B%20is%20one%20of%20several%20status%20codes%20that%20items%20can%20have%20in%20Costco's%20inventory%20management%20system%2C%20which%20the%20company%20likes%20to%20keep%20lean%20and%20tight%20by%20clearing%20out%20unnecessary%20merchandise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20seasonal%20items%20will%20be%20deleted%20from%20the%20system%20temporarily%20until%20their%20time%20comes%20back%20around%2C%20or%20sometimes%20the%20specific%20format%20of%20a%20product%20is%20changing%2C%20such%20as%20Bud%20Light%20in%2016-ounce%20cans%20versus%2012-ounce%20ones%2C%20each%20of%20which%20has%20a%20particular%20SKU.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20an%20asterisk%20on%20Bud%20Light%20products%20led%20to%20rumors%20that%20Costco%20was%20giving%20the%20%26quot%3Bstar%20of%20death%26quot%3B%20treatment%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbud-light-transgender-controversy-backlash-boycotts-history%5C%22%3EBud%20Light%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20conservative%20boycott%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20closer%20inspection%20of%20the%20signage%20showed%20that%20only%2016-ounce%20cans%20of%20Bud%20Light%20and%2012-ounce%20bottles%20of%20Bud%20Light%20Platinum%20were%20getting%20the%20star%20of%20death%20treatment.%20Cases%20of%2012-ounce%20cans%20of%20the%20mainstay%20beer%20still%20seem%20to%20be%20in%20Costco's%20replenishment%20queue%2C%20per%20screenshots%20of%20the%20inventory%20management%20system%20seen%20by%20Insider.%20Costco%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20questions%20regarding%20the%20status%20of%20Bud%20Light%20in%20its%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Costco%20sells%20through%20its%20inventory%2C%20its%20buyers%20determine%20whether%20to%20order%20more%20or%20let%20it%20go%20to%20zero.%20If%20they%20choose%20the%20latter%2C%20they%20mark%20the%20item%20as%20%26quot%3Bpending%20delete%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20system%2C%20and%20an%20asterisk%20is%20added%20to%20the%20item's%20price%20card%20to%20be%20printed%20and%20hung%20up%20the%20next%20morning.%20Sometimes%20the%20item%20is%20marked%20down%2C%20but%20not%20always.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20one%20little%20symbol%2C%20buyers%20can%20communicate%20with%20store%20managers%20across%20the%20country%20and%20help%20them%20plan%20ahead%2C%20the%20Texas%20manager%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20walking%20your%20aisles%20every%20day%20as%20a%20merchant%20manager%2C%20and%20you%20see%20'Oh%2C%20that%20items%20pending%20delete%2C%20I've%20only%20got%20that%20last%20pallet%20right%20here%2C'%20you%20can%20start%20making%20plans%20for%20how%20to%20fill%20that%20gap%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20every%20deleted%20product%20is%20gone%20forever%2C%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20some%20items%20that%20get%20deleted%20won't%20come%20back%2C%20in%20which%20case%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20grab%20what%20you%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20kind%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20thumb%20at%20Costco%3A%20if%20you%20see%20it%20now%2C%20buy%20it%20now%2C%20because%20I%20can't%20promise%20you%20it'll%20be%20here%20the%20next%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Texas%20manager%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EAre%20you%20a%20Costco%20employee%20who%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20perspective%3F%20Get%20in%20touch%20with%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Adreuter%40insider.com%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22mailto%3Adreuter%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EDominick%20via%20email%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%C2%A0or%20encrypted%20app%20Signal%20at%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E646.768.4750%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E.%20Insider%20recommends%20using%20a%20non-work%20device%20to%20reach%20out%2C%20and%20responses%20will%20be%20kept%20confidential.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20origina