%25%20to%2020%25%20gratuity%20on%20the%20total%20cost%20of%20a%20delivery%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOthers%20say%20percentage-based%20tips%20don't%20always%20account%20for%20the%20time%20and%20effort%20some%20deliveries%20take.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20recently%20asked%2010%20delivery%20drivers%20to%20weigh%20in%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcustomers-being-asked-to-tip-everywhere-theyre-sick-of-it-2023-3%5C%22%3Ehotly%20contested%20issue%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-to-tip-food-delivery-driver-doordash-ubereats-2023-7%5C%22%3EHow%20much%20should%20you%20tip%20on%20a%20%2420%20food%20delivery%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20stemmed%20from%20a%20recent%20incident%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-doordash-delivery-worker-tipping-culture-america-2023-7%5C%22%3EDoorDash%20fired%20a%20driver%20who%20cursed%20at%20a%20woman%20for%20tipping%20%245%20on%20a%20%2420%20order%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drivers%20Insider%20interviewed%20generally%20agreed%20that%20the%20baseline%20for%20a%20good%20tip%20is%20between%2015%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20the%20total%20bill%20%E2%80%94%20including%20taxes%20and%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20publishing%20our%20story%2C%20however%2C%20several%20current%20and%20former%20drivers%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-uber-eats-grubhub-sue-new-york-city-minimum-wage-2023-7%5C%22%3EDoorDash%2C%20Grubhub%2C%20Uber%20Eats%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20delivery%20platforms%20emailed%20us%20saying%20the%20article%20missed%20a%20key%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPercentage-based%20tips%20don't%20always%20account%20for%20the%20time%20and%20effort%20it%20takes%20to%20deliver%20an%20order%2C%20drivers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsider%20delivery%20time%20and%20distance%20when%20tipping%2C%20drivers%20say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20a%20%245%20tip%20on%20a%20%2420%20order%20is%20good%20(or%20bad)%20can%20depend%20on%20the%20circumstances%20of%20the%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20routes%2C%20traffic%2C%20difficulty%20parking%2C%20and%20restaurant%20delays%20can%20all%20make%20that%20%245%20less%20valuable%2C%20drivers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20customers%20should%20consider%20boosting%20tips%20for%20longer%20delivery%20routes%2C%20they%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDashers%20like%20me%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20earn%20a%20minimum%20hourly%20do%20not%20select%20orders%20based%20on%20whether%20or%20not%20the%20tip%20is%20proportional%20to%20their%20total%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20Navi%20Vong%2C%20a%20delivery%20driver%20who%20works%20for%20both%20DoorDash%20and%20Uber%20Eats%2C%20told%20Insider%20by%20email.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20we%20select%20orders%20based%20on%20distance%20to%20the%20customer%20and%20how%20much%20the%20total%20offer%20is.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20New%20York%20City%20%E2%80%94%20or%20at%20least%20the%20financial%20district%20of%20Manhattan%20where%20we%20conducted%20our%20initial%20driver%20survey%20%E2%80%94%20distances%20can%20be%20nominal.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20ordered%20coffee%20from%20a%20Starbucks%20that%20was%20roughly%20400%20feet%20from%20Insider's%20office.%20If%20you%20estimate%20an%20arbitrary%20base%20pay%20of%20%242%20and%20our%20tip%20of%20%242.50%2C%20drivers%20could%20earn%20around%20%244.50%20on%20an%20order%20that%20took%20maybe%2010%20minutes%20to%20complete.%20That%20could%20amount%20to%20%2427%20an%20hour%20if%20a%20driver%20could%20nab%20five%20other%20similar%20jobs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20though%2C%20where%20the%20distance%20between%20a%20customer%20and%20a%20restaurant%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20miles%2C%20the%20calculus%20changes%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20for%20drivers%20paying%20for%20gas%20and%20vehicle%20wear-and-tear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCouriers%20use%20their%20own%20vehicles%2C%20complete%20with%20insurance%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20other%20maintenance%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20Vong%20wrote.%20In%20the%20Phoenix%20area%20where%20Vong%20works%2C%20earning%20less%20than%20roughly%20%2420%20per%20hour%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20enough%20for%20the%20cost%20it%20takes%20to%20maintain%20the%20vehicle%20to%20deliver%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20drivers%20said%20they%20are%20constantly%20analyzing%C2%A0%20distance%2C%20travel%20times%2C%20and%20wait%20times%20in%20order%20to%20maximize%20their%20hourly%20earnings.%20Some%20have%20even%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-drivers-want-extra-tips-before-delivery-customers-complain-2023-5%5C%22%3Easking%20customers%20for%20higher%20tips%20before%20delivery.%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Though%20customers%20sometimes%20promise%20a%20big%20tip%2C%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-ceo-became-undercover-boss-used-tesla-surprised-rude-riders-2023-4%5C%22%3Ereduce%20it%20later%20in%20a%20practice%20called%20tip-baiting%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeaven%20Leigh%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Arizona%2C%20told%20Insider%20she%20drives%20for%20DoorDash%20outside%20of%20her%20full-time%20job%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20She%20often%20considers%20restaurants'%20speediness%20when%20weighing%20whether%20to%20accept%20a%20delivery%20offer%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20certain%20restaurants%20I%20decline%20every%20time%20because%20I%20know%20it%20will%20take%20too%20long%20for%20me%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20food%2C%20so%20if%20I%20end%20up%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20the%20drop%20off%20takes%20too%20long%20it%20can%20be%20devastating%20when%20I%20know%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffood-delivery-drivers-say-customers-dont-tip-enough-make-living-2023-4%5C%22%3Emy%20car%20payment%20is%20