ey%C2%A0to%20the%20pandemic's%20impact%20on%20the%20workforce%20%E2%80%94%20as%20some%20people%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-entrepreneurs-launched-started-grew-businesses-at-home-during-pandemic%5C%22%3Ecreate%20their%20own%20businesses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20those%20impacted%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fin-the-covid-economy-laid-off-employees-become-new-entrepreneurs-11605716565%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epandemic%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He's%20happy%20he%20gets%20to%20help%20small%20businesses%20%26quot%3Bget%20protection%20for%20their%20brands%2C%26quot%3B%20something%20he%20said%20he%20has%20a%20passion%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Morgan%20had%20been%20on%20Fiverr%20since%202019%2C%20he%20said%20he%20wasn't%20really%20using%20it.%20He%20actually%20got%20started%20in%20trademark-attorney%20work%20during%20the%20pandemic%20while%20working%20for%20a%20law%20firm.%20His%20cousin%20asked%20for%20his%20help%20in%20filing%20a%20trademark%2C%20as%20he%20had%20expertise%20in%20intellectual%20property%20from%20his%20studies%20in%20law%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20always%20had%20the%20knowledge%20and%20the%20skillset%2C%20but%20I%20wasn't%20really%20putting%20it%20to%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20helping%20his%20cousin%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20could%20probably%20offer%20these%20services%20elsewhere%20because%20it%20doesn't%20really%20interfere%20with%20the%20firm%2C%20with%20the%20work%20that%20I%20was%20doing%20at%20my%20law%20firm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20checking%20with%20his%20boss%2C%20he%20then%20spent%20time%20working%20for%20both%20the%20law%20firm%20he%20was%20working%20for%20%E2%80%94%20where%20his%20focus%20was%20sports%20law%20and%20litigation%20but%20also%20did%20civil%20rights%20work%20%E2%80%94%20and%20doing%20side%20work%20as%20a%20trademark%20attorney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEventually%20it%20just%20became%20too%20much%20to%20have%20two%20full-time%20jobs%20essentially%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20working%20nonstop%2C%20and%20then%20also%20I%20was%20out%20earning%20my%20law%20firm%20pay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMorgan%20likes%20being%20a%20digital%20nomad%20working%20from%20different%20places%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20was%20already%20able%20to%20travel%20while%20he%20was%20employed%20by%20the%20law%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20take%20three%20international%20trips%20a%20year%20just%20because%20I%20had%20the%20flexibility%20with%20my%20law%20firm%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20wanted%20to%20kind%20of%20keep%20doing%20that%20more%20and%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFreelance%20work%20allowed%20him%20to%20continue%20traveling.%20He%20tends%20to%20split%20his%20time%20between%20Mexico%20City%20and%20Chicago%20but%20also%20travels%20elsewhere.%20While%20he%20enjoys%20location%20flexibility%2C%20he%20says%20he%20usually%20works%20from%208%20a.m.%20to%206%20p.m.%20but%20%26quot%3Bthat's%20more%20so%20by%20choice%26quot%3B%20given%20clients%20being%20in%20different%20time%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20days%20are%20starting%20at%20different%20times%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20them%20what's%20the%20most%20efficient%20service%2C%20I%20will%20work%20later%20than%20I%20would%20at%20my%209-to-5%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20works%20a%20few%20hours%20on%20the%20weekends.%20But%20his%20schedule%20can%20also%20be%20flexible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221789%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20Derrick%20Morgan%20Jr.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64bc68d0bea34400195f45ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222691%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDerrick%20Morgan%20Jr.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Derrick%20Morgan%20Jr.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%20this%20year%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Asia%2C%20I%20wasn't%20really%20working%20in%20the%20morning%20because%20the%20time%20zone%20was%20so%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20was%20in%20the%20morning%20in%20Asia%2C%20people%20are%20asleep%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20is%20where%20most%20of%20my%20clients%20are.%20I%20had%20the%20mornings%20open%2C%20I'd%20go%20surfing%2C%20I'd%20go%20paddle%20boarding.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EMorgan%20said%20when%20he%20travels%2C%20he's%20usually%20heading%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.selina.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESelina%20location%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20a%20coworking%20hostel.%20He%20said%20it%20can%20be%20harder%20for%20him%20to%20meet%20people%20at%20a%20hotel%20and%20instead%20easier%20at%20coworking%20spaces.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20was%20a%20Work%20from%20Anywhere%20contest%20winner%20from%20a%20partnership%20between%20Fiverr%20and%20Selina.%20As%20a%20contest%20winner%2C%20that%20included%20%26quot%3B%242%2C000%20in%20cash%20voucher%20for%20travel%20expenses%20from%20Fiverr%2C%20as%20well%20as%20250%2C000%20Selina%20tokens%20(equivalent%20to%20approximately%20%242%2C000%20USD%20worth%20of%20overnight%20stays%20and%20other%20services%20at%20Selina%20locations%20)%20to%20redeem%20in%20Selina%20accommodations%2C%20wellness%20activities%2C%20and%20hot-desk%20access%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dccd2df61a67c00a688d0e5dbb9243dd6c9abef768f9ad9fdfa40c7ad5e5798d9%26postID%3D64ba8ac1818c7a7ff1df4031%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.fiverr.com%252Fnews%252Fselina-partnership%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMorgan%20suggests%20others%20who%20want%20to%20make%20a%20similar%20career%20change%20to%20try%20freelancing%20while%20holding%20a%20full-time%20position%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20want%20to%20make%20freelancing%20their%20full-time%20job%2C%20Morgan%20advises%20trying%20it%20out%20while%20employed%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20better%20to%20kind%20of%20start%20it%20while%20you%20have%20that%20full-time%20stability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20once%20you%20see%20that%20it's%20sustainable%2C%20kind%20of%20like%20how%20I%20did%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%20say%20I'm%20the%20blueprint%2C%20but%20it%20really%20worked%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20once%20you%20have%20that%20assurance%20that%20it's%20sustainable%2C%20however%20long%20that%20takes%2C%20then%20you%20can%20take%20that%20leap%20more%20comfortably%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDid%20you%20make%20a%20career%20switch%20during%20the%20pandemic%20or%20are%20you%20a%20digital%20nomad%20who%20gets%20to%20travel%20while%20working%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhoff%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emhoff%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20to%20share%20your%20story.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fattorney-lawyer-freelance-work-traveling-flexible-location-six-figures-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690107601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ba8c4303c40c001a97a4c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fattorney-lawyer-freelance-work-traveling-flexible-location-six-figures-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Derrick%20Morgan%20Jr.%20first%20thought%20freelancing%20on%20Fiverr%20while%20working%20at%20a%20law%20firm%20would%20help%20with%20bills.%20He's%20made%20over%20%24140%2C000%20so%20far%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Madison%20Hoff)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonical