of%20the%20Meitei%20community%20surfaced%20amidst%20their%20exodus%20triggered%20by%20an%20%26quot%3Badvisory%26quot%3B%20from%20a%20former%20militants'%20association%20in%20Mizoram.%20The%20advisory%20was%20in%20response%20to%20escalating%20tension%20resulting%20from%20a%20viral%20video%20showing%20two%20tribal%20women%20being%20stripped%20and%20paraded%20naked%20by%20a%20mob%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Home%20Commissioner%20and%20Secretary%20H%20Lalengmawia%20met%20with%20leaders%20of%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20assuring%20them%20of%20their%20safety%20and%20security%2C%20according%20to%20an%20official%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproximately%201%2C500%20Meitei%20families%20are%20known%20to%20reside%20and%20work%20across%20Mizoram%2C%20according%20to%20official%20sources.%20There%20have%20been%20widespread%20reports%20of%20Meiteis%20leaving%20the%20capital%20city%2C%20Aizawl%2C%20by%20various%20modes%20of%20transportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20influential%20civil%20society%20group%2C%20the%20Central%20Young%20Mizo%20Association%20(CYMA)%2C%20has%20also%20encouraged%20the%20Meiteis%20to%20live%20peacefully.%20The%20Mizo%20Students%20Union%20(MZU)%20has%20decided%20to%20halt%20its%20proposed%20drive%20to%20collect%20data%20about%20Meiteis%20in%20Mizoram%20after%20discussions%20with%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outrage%20in%20Mizoram%20over%20the%20viral%20video%20of%20two%20tribal%20women%20being%20sexually%20assaulted%20in%20Manipur%20led%20to%20panic%20among%20the%20small%20community%20of%20Meiteis%20residing%20in%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20government%20has%20expressed%20willingness%20to%20evacuate%20them%20from%20the%20state%20via%20chartered%20flight%20if%20the%20situation%20deteriorates.%20However%2C%20no%20attack%20on%20the%20Meitei%20community%20has%20been%20reported%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mizos%20of%20Mizoram%2C%20who%20share%20a%20deep%20ethnic%20bond%20with%20the%20Kuki-Zomis%20of%20Manipur%2C%20have%20been%20providing%20shelter%20and%20care%20to%20over%2012%2C000%20Kuki-Zomi%20people%20who%20fled%20from%20Manipur%20since%20violence%20erupted%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Peace%20Accord%20MNF%20Returnees'%20Association%20(PAMRA)%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20Friday%2C%20suggesting%20that%20Meiteis%20should%20leave%20Mizoram%20for%20their%20%26quot%3Bown%20safety%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPAMRA%20cited%20%26quot%3Banger%20among%20Mizo%20youth%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20incident%20involving%20the%20two%20women%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20state%20as%20the%20reason.%20They%20added%20that%20any%20potential%20violence%20against%20the%20Meiteis%20in%20Mizoram%20would%20solely%20be%20their%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20PAMRA%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20in%20Mizoram%20has%20become%20tense%2C%20and%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20safe%20for%20Meitei%20people%20from%20Manipur%20to%20live%20in%20Mizoram...%26quot%3B.%20They%20appealed%20to%20all%20Meitei%20people%20in%20Mizoram%20to%20return%20to%20their%20home%20state%20as%20a%20safety%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEthnic%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20at%20least%20125%20people%20and%20over%2040%2C000%20have%20fled%20their%20homes%20since%20violence%20erupted%20on%20May%203.%20The%20conflict%20began%20between%20the%20Kuki%20tribal%20group%20and%20the%20Meitei%2C%20a%20non-tribal%20ethnic%20majority%2C%20over%20disputes%20regarding%20economic%20benefits%20and%20quotas%20allocated%20to%20tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20violence%20was%20initially%20quelled%20after%20the%20central%20government%20deployed%20thousands%20of%20paramilitary%20and%20army%20troops%20to%20the%20state%20of%203.2%20million%20people%2C%20sporadic%20violence%20resumed%20shortly%20thereafter.%20The%20state%20has%20remained%20tense%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690107000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvi