0an%20annual%20festival%20held%20every%20July%20in%20southern%20Ladakh%2C%20located%20close%20to%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20release%2C%20the%20MHA%E2%80%99s%20July%2013%20permission%20is%20specific%20to%20the%20two-day%20Ladakh%20Nomadic%20Festival%20held%20annually%20in%20Hanle%2C%20the%20largest%20village%20in%20that%20part%20of%20Ladakh%20under%20the%20Nyoma%20sub-division%20of%20the%20union%20territory.%20The%20Nyoma%20sub-division%20includes%20the%20sensitive%20Demchok%20village%20along%20the%20Chinese%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPermitting%20foreign%20tourists%20to%20visit%20frontier%20areas%20like%20Hanle%20in%20particular%20and%20the%20Changthang%20region%20in%20general%20had%20been%20a%20long-standing%20demand%20of%20the%20Ladakh%20Autonomous%20Hill%20District%20Council%20(LAHDC).%20Till%20now%2C%20foreign%20tourists%20were%20allowed%20only%20till%20Nyoma%2C%20situated%20about%2057%20kms%20from%20Hanle.%20Even%20Indian%20tourists%20are%20required%20to%20take%20inner%20line%20permits%20to%20visit%20these%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%E2%80%99s%20festival%20at%20Hanle%20was%20the%20third%20edition%2C%20organised%20annually%20mid-July%2C%20by%20the%20Ladakh%20Art%20Culture%20and%20Languages%20Academy.%20The%20festival%20promotes%20the%20art%2C%20craft%2C%20food%20and%20culture%20of%20the%20local%20Changpa%20tribe%2C%20and%20is%20aimed%20at%20offering%20a%20platform%20to%20the%20nomadic%20population%20to%20sell%20their%20wares%20to%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20reports%20said%20the%20organisers%2C%20while%20welcoming%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%2C%20hoped%20that%20foreign%20tourists%20are%20allowed%20to%20visit%20and%20stay%20in%20Hanle%20and%20other%20areas%20of%20Changthang%20beyond%20the%20annual%20festival%20so%20that%20tourism%20in%20that%20remote%20area%20could%20expand%20to%20become%20a%20steady%20source%20of%20income%20for%20the%20local%20population.%20The%20MHA%E2%80%99s%20July%2013%20decision%20was%20taken%20after%20getting%20a%20go%20ahead%20from%20the%20Army%20which%2C%20news%20reports%20said%2C%20was%20arrived%20at%20after%20consultations%20with%20the%20festival%20organisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20permission%20was%20granted%20just%20two%20days%20before%20the%20festival%20was%20to%20start%2C%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20foreign%20tourists%20could%20visit%20the%20festival.%20When%20The%20Wire%20visited%20it%20on%20July%2016%2C%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20festival%2C%20only%20a%20few%20foreign%20tourists%20could%20be%20spotted.%20Some%20visitors%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20they%20were%20already%20in%20Leh%20and%20decided%20travel%20to%20Hanle%20upon%20coming%20to%20know%20about%20the%20lifting%20of%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeld%20at%20a%20sprawling%20field%20in%20Hanle%20under%20an%20azure%20sky%2C%20the%20festival%20was%20a%20colourful%20sight%2C%20full%20of%20local%20flavour.%20Songs%20and%20dances%20of%20the%20tribe%2C%20their%20craft%20and%20way%20of%20life%20were%20exhibited%20for%20visitors.%20A%20wide%20array%20of%20local%20food%20was%20a%20special%20attraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20peek%20at%20the%20fest%20through%20eight%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23124608%2FImage-1-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23124608%2FImage-1-1.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23124608%2FImage-1-1-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23124608%2FImage-1-1-768x1024.jpg