to%20stop%20the%20violence.%20The%20women%20left%20the%20spot%20later%20on%20their%20own%2C%20she%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanja%20also%20added%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cno%20need%20to%20politicise%E2%80%9D%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20incident%20has%2C%20however%2C%20fast%20become%20a%20political%20issue%20in%20the%20state%2C%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20claiming%20that%20the%20attacked%20women%20belonged%20to%20a%20tribal%20community%2C%20a%20claim%20that%20is%20being%20challenged%20by%20the%20CPI(M).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20video%20of%20two%20Manipur%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20in%20Thoubal%20district%20created%20nationwide%20ripples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690044627000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F22221426%2FUntitled-design-4-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbengal-police-arrest-5-after-video-shows-women-being-paraded-naked-brutally-assaulted-in-malda%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20daughter%20of%20one%20of%20the%20attacked%20women%20has%20alleged%20that%20no%20proper%20medical%20attention%20was%20given%20to%20her%20mother%20and%20the%20other%20women%2C%20and%20instead%20they%20were%20both%20taken%20into%20custody.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbengal-police-arrest-5-after-video-shows-women-being-paraded-naked-brutally-assaulted-in-malda%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jamie%20Foxx%20Tears%20Up%20Thanking%20His%20Family%20in%20First%20Video%20to%20Fans%20Discussing%20Hospitalization%3A%20%E2%80%98I%20Just%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Want%20You%20to%20See%20Me%20Like%2