dar%20(Yamuna%20Bank)%20area%20are%20now%20homeless%20and%20stuck%20under%20dehumanising%20conditions%20in%20Mayur%20Vihar%20Flood%20Relief%20Camp%2C%20waiting%20to%20return%20to%20their%20homes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBad%20urban%20planning%20is%20responsible%20for%20our%20conditions%2C%20we%20are%20always%20excluded.%20You%20see%2C%20the%20posh%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20are%20never%20drowned.%20And%20even%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20water%20in%20those%20places%2C%20they%20do%20not%20face%20the%20torment%20that%20we%20face.%20Rich%20people%20never%20suffer%20from%20these%20curses.%20We%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20are%20perennially%20subjected%20to%20this.%E2%80%99%E2%80%99%20says%20Sangeeta%20(16)%2C%20a%20student%20of%2011th%20standard.%20She%20wanted%20to%20become%20an%20IAS%20officer%20but%20is%20now%20cynical%20about%20it%20since%20the%20flood%20has%20destroyed%20almost%20everything%20that%20their%20family%20had%2C%20leaving%20them%20to%20start%20their%20life%20all%20over%20again%20from%20scratch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20gave%20us%20any%20warning%20about%20the%20flood.%20There%20was%20no%20official%20announcement%20or%20information.%20All%20my%20books%20were%20drowned.%20Books%20are%20expensive%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20money%20to%20buy%20them%20again.%20I%20am%20going%20to%20school%20from%20this%20relief%20camp%20these%20days%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20books.%20What%20will%20I%20study%3F%20And%20how%20will%20I%20study%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20poor%20people%20but%20we%20are%20also%20residents%20of%20Delhi.%20And%20that%20too%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Our%20fathers%20and%20grandfathers%20have%20lived%20in%20these%20lands.%20We%20gave%20everything%20to%20Delhi.%20We%20built%20the%20city%2C%20we%20grew%20the%20crops.%20We%20spent%20all%20our%20lives%20cleaning%20rich%20people%E2%80%99s%20houses.%20But%20now%20as%20we%20are%20stranded%20in%20these%20camps%2C%20nobody%20has%20any%20problem%20with%20it.%20The%20government%20has%20no%20value%20for%20us.%20Will%20the%20government%20officials%20eat%20the%20food%20that%20we%20are%20getting%20here%3F%20They%20won%E2%80%99t.%20Because%20this%20food%20is%20made%20for%20poor%20people.%20They%20expect%20us%20to%20shut%20our%20mouths%20even%20after%20all%20these.%20There%20is%20no%20relief%20at%20this%20relief%20camp!%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sonia%20Devi%20(44)%20who%20used%20to%20work%20as%20an%20agricultural%20labourer%20prior%20to%20the%20flood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F22195606%2FCGR-3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F22195606%2FCGR-3.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F22195606%2FCGR-3-300x235.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F22195606%2FCGR-3-1024x802.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664586%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22940%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBittu%20(21)%2C%20a%20YouTuber%20and%20video%20editor%2C%20while%20resenting%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20inaction%20and%20carelessness%20about%20flood%20victims%2C%20says%20%E2%80%9CNobody%20came%20to%20rescue%20us%20when%20the%20floods%20hit%20our%20settlements.%20We%20reached%20this%20relief%20camp%20on%20our%20own.%20We%20had%20to%20make%20boats%20using%20banana%20trees.%20People%20have%20walked%20through%20the%20waters%20at%20neck%20levels%20carrying%20little%20kids%20on%20their%20shoulders.%20We%20