findia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fimphal%2Fon-day-of-manipur-mob-horror-2-gang-raped-killed-40km-away%2Farticleshow%2F102024469.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20male%20friend%20of%20the%20women%2C%20who%20saw%20an%20ambulance%20pick%20them%20up%2C%20reached%20the%20hospital%20the%20next%20day%20and%20was%20told%20they%20had%20succumbed%20to%20the%20injuries.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20dragged%20one%20of%20them%20inside%2C%20switched%20off%20the%20lights%2C%20and%20took%20turns%20raping%20her.%20Then%20they%20did%20the%20same%20to%20my%20other%20co-worker.%20They%20gagged%20both%20with%20clothes%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20screaming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20women%20in%20that%20particular%20mob%20encouraged%20men%20to%20take%20the%20women%20into%20a%20room%20and%20assault%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%2C%20the%20women%20were%20dragged%20out%20of%20the%20room%20and%20were%20dumped%20near%20a%20sawmill%20in%20the%20vicinity.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20clothes%20were%20torn%2C%20their%20hair%20chopped%20off%2C%20and%20their%20bodies%20covered%20in%20blood%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20man%2C%20also%20a%20tribal%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20conveyed%20the%20information%20to%20a%20cousin%20of%20one%20of%20the%20women%20who%20was%20hiding%20in%20a%20church%20to%20escape%20the%20clashes%20outside.%20It%20was%20only%20when%20the%20cousin%20in%20question%20was%20evacuated%20to%20Kangpokpi%20by%20Assam%20Rifles%20the%20families%20of%20the%20women%20got%20to%20know%20of%20what%20had%20happened%20to%20their%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-imphal-violence-daughters-killed%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20a%20detailed%20account%20by%20the%20fathers%20of%20the%20women%20%E2%80%93%20the%20women%20were%20aged%2021%20and%2024.%20The%20report%20was%20pub