-hyperspectral-satellite-launch-hyperloop-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Raipur%20Boy%20in%20Mumbai%20Paved%20the%20Way%20for%20Chhattisgarhi%20Cinema%20with%20His%20Historic%20Film%20on%20Caste%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20films%20that%20leave%20their%20mark%20in%20time%2C%20and%20Shyam%20Benegal%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EAnkur%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1974)%20is%20one%20classic%20example.%20The%20film%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20extend%20beyond%20the%20confines%20of%20bagging%20three%20National%20Awards.%20Through%20its%20gripping%20storyline%2C%20it%20sparked%20debate%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F96444%2Fsadri-behenchara-overcome-caste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20caste%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20its%20evils%20in%20India%20through%20the%20optics%20of%20those%20most%20victimised%20by%20its%20effects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20highlights%20the%20arc%20of%20emotions%20that%20Lakshmi%20(a%20Dalit%20woman%20living%20in%20rural%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20essayed%20by%20Shabana%20Azmi)%20goes%20through%20as%20she%20begins%20working%20for%20an%20upper-caste%20%3Cem%3Ezamindar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20son%20Surya%2C%20who%20does%20not%20delve%20too%20much%20into%20the%20caste%20difference.%20The%20movie%20brings%20to%20the%20front%20issues%20of%20patriarchy%2C%20caste%2C%20class%20and%20gender%20in%20a%20tale%20that%20is%20both%20beautiful%20and%20sad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20decades%2C%20Indian%20cinema%20has%20touched%20upon%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F16955%2Fmen-silently-building-caste-less-india-one-child-time%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epervasive%20caste%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20through%20many%20films%20%E2%80%94%20some%20deemed%20controversial%20yet%20milestones%2C%20like%20%