-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-5-1689943704.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-5-1689943704-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-5-1689943704-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-5-1689943704-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324751%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20movie%20poster%20of%20Kahi%20Debe%20Sandesh%20(1965)%20by%20Manu%20Nayak%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wikipedia%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrawanshi%20wrote%20that%20Nayak%E2%80%99s%20motive%20behind%20making%20this%20film%20was%20as%20follows%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKahi%20Debe%20Sandes%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1965)%20is%20a%20commentary%20on%20social%20issues%20such%20as%20Untouchability%20and%20Caste%20discrimination.%20I%20had%20seen%20it%20happening%20even%20in%20my%20own%20house.%20Whenever%20my%20friends%20from%20the%20lower%20castes%20(Satnami%20caste)%20used%20to%20come%20to%20my%20home%2C%20my%20mother%20used%20to%20not%20say%20anything%20but%20soon%20after%20they%20had%20left%20she%20used%20to%20clean%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20house.%20This%20and%20a%20few%20other%20instances%20deeply%20affected%20me%20and%20I%20realised%20that%20until%20caste%20discrimination%20is%20addressed%20properly%20to%20the%20masses%2C%20society%20would%20not%20progress.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20intent%20on%20these%20issues%20seeing%20the%20light%20of%20day%2C%20Nayak%20began%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291630%2Fsanober-pardiwalla-bollywood-stuntwoman-for-actress-alia-bhatt-deepika-padukone-movies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equest%20of%20casting%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20song%20recorded%