ing%20classes%20to%20teach%20Indian%20cuisine%20to%20foreign%20tourists.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324596%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShashi%20runs%20cooking%20classes%20to%20teach%20Indian%20cuisine%20to%20foreign%20tourists.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20next%20class%2C%20there%20were%20French%20tourists.%20They%20did%20not%20know%20English%20and%20I%20did%20not%20know%20French.%20They%20would%20look%20at%20my%20face%2C%20I%20would%20look%20at%20theirs!%20If%20they%20said%20%3Cem%3Edekho%3C%2Fem%3E%20(%3Cem%3Ed%E2%80%99accord%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20French%20means%20%E2%80%98okay%E2%80%99%20and%20%3Cem%3Edekho%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Hindi%20means%20%E2%80%98see%E2%80%99)%2C%20I%20would%20start%20staring%20at%20places%20and%20everyone%20would%20burst%20into%20laughter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20amidst%20giggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20language%20barriers%2C%20Shashi%20received%20much%20affection%20from%20foreign%20guests%20who%20also%20tried%20to%20teach%20her%20their%20languages.%20From%20knowing%20only%20Rajasthani%2C%20she%20can%20now%20speak%20basic%20words%20in%20English%20and%20several%20other%20foreign%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20learn%20these%20languages%20because%2C%20without%20that%2