m%20excited%20to%20use%20everything%20I%20learned%20from%20Shashi%E2%80%99s%20class%20in%20Spain.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20definitely%20put%20those%20skills%20into%20practice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20a%20five-hour%20class%2C%20the%20guests%20relish%20the%20cooked%20meals.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324597%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20a%20five-hour%20class%2C%20the%20guests%20relish%20the%20cooked%20meals.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20focus%20is%20not%20to%20only%20earn%20an%20income%20from%20these%20guests%20but%20also%20to%20treat%20them%20nicely%20because%20they%20are%20our%20guests.%20They%20should%20be%20happy%20when%20they%20go%20back%20to%20their%20homes.%20Sometimes%2C%20they%20even%20pay%20me%20extra%20on%20their%20own%20out%20of%20love.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20delectable%20meals%2C%20these%20tourists%20also%20enjoy%20Shashi%E2%80%99s%20company%2C%20who%20does%20not%20miss