%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-3-1689772598.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kids%20in%20her%20boarding%20school%20are%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%208%20to%2010%20years%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-3-1689772598.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-3-1689772598-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-3-1689772598-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-3-1689772598-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-3-1689772598-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324382%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPortia%20started%20with%20three%20children%20which%20has%20now%20grown%20to%2010.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Portia%20Putatunda%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20started%20her%20boarding%20school%20with%20three%20children%20and%20the%20number%20has%20grown%20to%2010%20presently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20herself%20%E2%80%9Cmother%E2%80%9D%20to%20those%20children%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20children%20are%20not%20orphans%20and%20are%20not%20abandoned%20by%20choice%20but%20by%20poverty.%20Around%2050%20percent%20of%20these%20kids%20do%20not%20have%20a%20surviving%20parent%2C%20but%20the%20rest%20have%20parents%20who%20can%E2%80%99t%20raise%20them.%20This%20is%20where%20I%20come%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20children%20keep%20me%20going%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20morning%20Portia%20wakes%20up%20to%20the%20sound%20of%20the%20children%20outside%20her%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20would%20call%20me%20Portia%20madam%20and%20giggle%20at%