began%20to%20explore%20this%20new%20arena%20of%20interest%2C%20marvelling%20at%20how%20a%20parasite%20could%20cause%20human%20disease%20by%20infecting%20a%20mosquito.%20Armed%20with%20this%20awe-evoking%20information%20Ross%20began%20his%20work%20on%20proving%20that%20malaria%20was%20connected%20to%20mosquitoes%20in%201895.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20an%20able%20assistant%2C%20he%20came%20across%20the%20keen%20Bandyopadhyay%20who%20was%20looking%20for%20work%20as%20a%20lab%20assistant.%20In%201898%2C%20the%20two%20bonded%20over%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F118874%2Fnew-malaria-detection-kit-costs-only-rs-10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassion%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20it%20was%20a%20done%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBandyopadhyay%20would%20assist%20Ross.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20years%20spanning%20between%201898%20and%201902%20were%20brimming%20with%20research%20ideas%20that%20the%20two%20men%20of%20science%20had.%20While%20Ross%20would%20get%20excited%20over%20new%20developments%20in%20their%20quest%20to%20prove%20the%20relationship%20between%20mosquitoes%20and%20malaria%2C%20Bandyopadhyay%20made%20maximum%20use%20of%20his%20abilities%20in%20regional%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20necessitated%20testing%20the%20blood%20of%20malaria%20patients%2C%20observation%20and%20dissections%20of%20the%20female%20Anopheles%20mosquito%2C%20etc%2C%20and%20Bandyopadhyay%20would%20put%20his%20skills%20to%20the%20test.%20He%20would%20regularly%20visit%20the%20neighbouring%20villages%20of%20Kolkata%20and%20Madras%20in%20search%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F89643%2Fwhy-new-drug-development-priority-rare-disease-research%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epatients%20with%20malaria%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20bring%20them%20back%20to%20Ross%E2%80%99%20lab.%20Here%